RACE.RACE_TEXT: GULFSTREAM PARK RACE 1 5F All Weather Track CR: 65. Maiden Claiming Purse 28000. FOR MAIDENS, FILLIES TWO YEARS OLD. Weight, 118 lbs. Claiming Price $25,000.
RACE.FOOTNOTES: KAITIE KAIT prompted the pace in the five path, was roused to bid in the three path early around the turn, took the lead while drifting inward in upper stretch, and was driven clear in the final furlong. SKY DIVINE set the pace in the two path, was challenged by the outer eventual winner while along the inside around the three eighths, lost the lead turning into the lane, had to alter outside the in-drifting leader passing the eighth pole, and kept on for place. FIELD OF BLOSSOMS stalked in the five path, was under coaxing in the four path around the turn, and finished evenly from the five path down the stretch for show. WONDERFULVENEZUELA chased in the three path, was driven in the four path around the turn, got floated out to the eight path turning into the stretch, and made no impact. PANOLA rated from the rail, was coaxed in the three path rounding the turn, floated out to the seven path going into the stretch, but flattened. QUEEN AIKO tracked inside, but faded in the two path turning into the lane. HERMOSA MUJER raced off the pace in the four path, was cued in the five path early around the turn, but did not threaten. MAELSTROM SPIRIT broke out at the start, and always trailed from the five to two paths. NO CHANGES WERE MADE AFTER THE RIDER OF SKY DIVINE OBJECTED AGAINST THE RIDER OF KAITIE KAIT FOR INTERFERENCE AT THE EIGHTH POLE.
